兩架直升機各有4名乘客。<ref name=Stuff67186780/>起飛後的幾秒鐘，兩架直升機就在距離地面{{convert|100|m|ft}}的高度[[空中相撞|空中相撞]]<ref name=BBC31809231/>。事故發生在當地時間17時15分（[[UTC|UTC]]20時15分）左右。<ref name=Reuters100315>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/10/us-argentina-crash-idUSKBN0M52EH20150310 |title=French sports stars killed in Argentina helicopter crash |first1=Eliana |last1=Raszewski |first2=Mark |last2=John |publisher=Reuters |date=2015-03-10 |accessdate=2015-03-10 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924214150/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/10/us-argentina-crash-idUSKBN0M52EH20150310 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>兩架直升機上的10人全數於事故中死亡，死者包括有弗洛倫斯·阿爾托、卡米耶·米法，以及亞歷克西·瓦斯蒂納此三位參賽的法國運動員；<ref name=RT239121>{{cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/239121-helicopters-crash-argentina-french/ |title=French star athletes, TV crew among 10 dead in Argentina twin helicopter crash |publisher=RT |accessdate=2015-03-09 |archive-date=2016-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311074438/https://www.rt.com/news/239121-helicopters-crash-argentina-french/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>其餘死者為兩名阿根廷籍駕駛員，和5名法國籍的電視節目製作團隊人員。<ref name=BBC31809231/><ref name=Stuff67186780>{{cite web |url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/world/americas/67186780/ten-dead-in-double-helicopter-crash-in-argentina |title=Ten dead in double helicopter crash in Argentina |publisher=Stuff.co.nz |accessdate=2015-03-10 |archive-date=2018-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181107224824/https://www.stuff.co.nz/world/americas/67186780/ten-dead-in-double-helicopter-crash-in-argentina |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據報導，事故發生時的[[天氣|天氣]]良好；而其他參賽者當時正在附近的地面被矇上[[眼罩|眼罩]]等候著。<ref name=BBC31809231>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-31809231|title=Three French sports stars die in Argentina helicopter crash|date=2015-03-09|work=[[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]]|accessdate=2015-03-09|archive-date=2015-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150310010034/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-31809231|dead-url=no}}</ref>

兩名直升機師都是經驗老到，有三十年經驗，並且都是退役軍人。<ref name="francetvinfo 20150310">{{cite news|url=http://www.francetvinfo.fr/faits-divers/crash-en-argentine/ce-que-l-on-sait-des-deux-pilotes-morts-dans-le-crash-en-argentine_845921.html|title=Ce que l'on sait des deux pilotes morts dans le crash en Argentine|publisher=Francetvinfo|author=Carole Bélingard|date=2015-03-11|accessdate=2015-03-13|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124190303/https://www.francetvinfo.fr/faits-divers/crash-en-argentine/ce-que-l-on-sait-des-deux-pilotes-morts-dans-le-crash-en-argentine_845921.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

